外支持境外 esim 。</li>\n<li>非国行设备禁止安装国内 esim 。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>根据这个策略，有没有可能国内 App Store 账号也会如此限制，即：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>国行设备根据设备定位，仅在出境后允许登陆外区账号</li>\n<li>仅有国行设备支持大陆区账号。</li>\n</ol>\n","last_modified":1697784400,"replies":14,"id":983772},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":23978,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2754,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":511263,"username":"EyebrowsWhite","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/EyebrowsWhite","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/530c/66b8/511263_mini.png?m=1667208751","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/530c/66b8/511263_normal.png?m=1667208751","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/530c/66b8/511263_large.png?m=1667208751","created":1601955502,"last_modified":1667208751},"last_reply_by":"ailiaoke","last_touched":1697770313,"title":"iPhone 媒体音量无法静音","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/983664","created":1697766220,"deleted":0,"content":"放一段录屏在这里，https://i.imgur.com/q888jzy.mp4\r\n\r\n表现就是，我在软件页面通过音量按钮把音量降到最低之后，下拉控制中心，看到音量又升回去了一点，然后我在控制中心往下滑，滑到底之后立刻回弹。\r\n\r\n不知道这是 bug 还是 feature","content_rendered":"<p>放一段录屏在这里，<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/q888jzy.mp4\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://i.imgur.com/q888jzy.mp4</a></p>\n<p>表现就是，我在软件页面通过音量按钮把音量降到最低之后，下拉控制中心，看到音量又升回去了一点，然后我在控制中心往下滑，滑到底之后立刻回弹。</p>\n<p>不知道这是 bug 还是 feature</p>\n","last_modified":1697766220,"replies":14,"id":983664},{"node":{"avat